  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare medical and surgical treatments of benign prostate
      hyperplasia in patients who have non muscle invasive bladder cancer for tumour recurrence and
      progression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
